(44, 'Heads up note from @Aakash 2025-04-04T19:20:00.000+05:30: Sharing a brief note for our $50K investment in Ask My Guru’s pre-seed round, amounting to 0.6% ownership. This is a community cheque underwriting with Abhishek Goyal backing the co The co is raising $1.5 Mn at $8 M post money. Round is being led by Lumikai with participation from MPL This was brought to us by Sai at MPL and product was strongly vouched for with a strong reference on Krishna. We are restricting this to a community cheque given this is pre-traction. The founding team has strong FMF and knows the consumer tech growth playbook well. They are taking an AI first approach and launching first with astrology. About Co - Ask My Guru is building AI + human (expert) in the loep astrology platform - They are doing deep work on data set gathering around vedic shastras to unlock conversational AI for vedic astrology, vaastu and ayurveda and more - Building the platform in a co-bot approach of gurus (seasoned vedic experts) with their AI avatars Founding Team 1. Krishna Mohan 1. Vivek Sadamate - SVP Design at MPL - NID Ahmedabad grad Founder BRCs: The founders had strong soft refs from MPL (Sai, Shashank and  Shubh) : MPL is investing $300K from the balance sheet. Deeper BRCs we are running now as we form a view for a follow on investment Considerations - Experience operators with strong FMF and past experience of building and scaling consumer tech product - Unique differentiated arpproach to build for a large TAM Ri...'),
