(71, 'Ref from Priyans (CoFo): Context: Priyans was a CoFo of the Breethr founders in their prev company ActiveBuildings Notes: 1. Priyans is also involved in Breethr - more on back office 2. Priyans also runs an EV business - he is more focused there 3. Priyans and Abhinav met on BITS Goa campus in 2010 - filed patents together, research together and both decided to do something in hardware together 4. Pivoted to air quality in 2014 5. ActiveBuilding had a F&F round 6. Manav was hired around COVID (2020) when they were doing a Swiggy project - Manav had an inside sales background and was boots on ground in BLR 7. Abhinav and him are hands on founders 8. Peak was 30 employees in 3 cities 9. Peak revenue was ₹7 crore - ₹1 crore PAT 10. Sensor doesn''t make as much money as solutions 11. Abhinav was great at B2B deals eg Reliance NetMeds 12. NetMeds warehouse - temperature and humidity monitoring 13. Abhinav used to crack deal and then Priyans would do implementation 14. Still has positive relationship with Abhinav 15. Pandemic era - got $50L from DOD for Kavach grant 16. PAPR - Priyans and Abhinav built this solution, but by then PPE was in the vogue, army wanted something more sturdier 17. PAPR journey gave them an idea of how solutions are built 18. Started as distributors of air purifiers 19. Simple product is easy, sexy product needs capex investment 20. Closed a ₹2 crore order during pandemic for MI team (for ActiveBuilding) 21. Call center incident - Disprin stock was still wit...'),
